title: 'Boys and Girl - Playoff Chances, Late Season Optimism, Negotiating with Post-Injury Dak
itunes:title: 'Boys and Girl - Playoff Chances, Late Season Optimism, Negotiating with Post-Injury Dak
description:
On today’s episode of the 'Boys and Girl Podcast, Jane and Bobby discuss whether or not the Cowboys can actually make the playoffs in 2020, and what they might do if they get there. Plus, the duo dives into the Dak Prescott contract negotiation. Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys’ community.
